    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I've been thinking about the tension between religious freedom and state laws. Should religious organizations be allowed to opt-out of government mandates if those mandates conflict with their beliefs, or does that just undermine the secular nature of the state? Which way do you think is more important for a healthy society?",
